  "Code examples, JSON Schemas, and machine-readable policy templates are licensed under the MIT License unless otherwise stated. You may deploy them on your own sites freely.": "Dikao tsa khoutu, Disekema tsa JSON, le disampole tsa dipholisi tse di balwang ke metšhini di fiwa laesense ka fa tlase ga MIT License, fa go sa buiwa sengwe se sele. O ka di tsenya mo mafelong a gago ka mahala.",
  "Combined rights entry point": "Ntlha ya go tsena e e kopantsweng ya ditshwanelo",
