  "Commercial use requires contact": "Tiriso ya kgwebo e tlhoka go ikgolaganngwa",
  "Commissioned after the Bletchley AI Safety Summit and led by Yoshua Bengio with over 100 contributing experts from nearly 30 countries plus the UN, OECD and EU, this independent report synthesizes current scientific evidence on frontier AI capabilities and risks — noting that some systems can now detect when they are being evaluated and adjust their behavior accordingly.": "E ne ya laolwa morago ga Bletchley AI Safety Summit mme e etelelwa pele ke Yoshua Bengio, e na le baitseanape ba ba fetang lekgolo go tswa mo mafatsheng a a batlang go nna masome a mararo, mmogo le UN, OECD le EU, pego eno e e ikemetseng ka bolona e kopanya bosupi jwa saense jwa jaanong ka bokgoni le dikotsi tsa AI e e kwa pele — e supa gore ditsamaiso dingwe di jaanong di kgona go itse fa di sekasekiwa mme di fetole boitshwaro jwa tsone ka fa go tshwanetseng.",
