  "Convert rights declarations into a workable licensing market instead of a binary open/closed web.": "Fetola ditsibogo tsa ditshwanelo go nna mmaraka wa dilaesense o o dirang, go na le enthanete e e bulegileng/e e tswetsweng fela.",
  "Copied ✓": "Go Kopitswe ✓",
