  "Transformation": "Tefetolo",
  "Turns declared rights into executable licensing: quote, pay, verify, audit, revoke.": "E fetola ditshwanelo tse di tsibogilweng go nna kabo ya dilaesense e e diragadiwang: tekanyo ya theko, tuelo, netefatso, tlhotlhomiso, phimolo.",
  "Twenty languages live in total: English, Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese, Japanese, Korean, French, German, Spanish, Portuguese, Russian, Arabic, Turkish, Persian, Bengali, Hindi, Indonesian, Vietnamese, Greek, Italian, Dutch.": "Ka kakaretso diteme di le masome a mabedi di a dira: Sekgowa, Sechaena se se Tlwaelesegileng, Sechaena se se Nolofaditsweng, Sejapane, Sekorea, Sefora, Sejeremane, Sepanishi, Seporoketšhe, Serashea, Searabia, Seturkey, Sepersi, Sebengali, Sehindi, Seindonesia, Sevietnam, Sekgerika, Setaliana, Dutch.",
  "Two license tiers: a free public tier and a contact-based commercial tier.": "Maemo a mabedi a dilaesense: maemo a mahala a setšhaba le maemo a kgwebo a a ikaegileng ka go ikgolaganya.",
  "UI": "Sebopego sa Modirisi",
  "Undefined openness reads as legal uncertainty to AI pipelines and gets cleaned out; only protocolized, machine-readable permission makes content genuinely learnable.": "Bobulegi jo bo sa tlhalosiwang bo balega e le go sa itse ga semolao mo dithulaganyong tsa AI mme bo a tlosiwa; ke tetlelelo e e porotokolwang, e e balwang ke metšhini fela e e dirang gore diteng di kgone go ithutwa tota.",
  "Usage logs and audit trails": "Direkoto tsa Tiriso le Mekgwa ya Tlhotlhomiso",
