  "“AICL: AI Ingestion & Capability Layer” now published in English as the canonical edition; the Chinese original manuscript remains available and both versions cross-link.": "“AICL: AI Ingestion & Capability Layer” jaanong e phasaladitswe ka Sekgowa e le tokololo e e tlhomameng; mokwalo wa ntlha wa Sechaena o sa ntse o le teng mme ditokololo tse pedi di golagane.",
  "“Protocolized Openness” confirmed as an English-language paper (with Chinese parallel passages) — no separate translation planned.": "“Protocolized Openness” e netefaditswe e le pampiri ya teme ya Sekgowa (ka dikarolwana tsa Sechaena tse di tsamayang le yona) — ga go thanolo e nngwe e e ikaeletsweng.",
